```py
SELECT employee_name,
       exp,
       CASE WHEN exp > 4 THEN 'Is a Senior'
            ELSE NULL END AS exp_level
  FROM xyz.marketing_employees
```

```py
SELECT employee_name, exp_level,
FROM EMPLOYEE
GROUP BY experience
HAVING COUNT(experience) > 5;
```

```py
SELECT employee_name, exp_level,
FROM EMPLOYEE
WHERE experience=  5;
```
